\" /><br /><small>([[Broad Street Line|Broad Street (Orange)]],<br />[[Market\u2013Frankford Line|Market\u2013Frankford (Blue)]], and [[Norristown High Speed Line|Norristown High Speed]] Lines)</small>\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | {{flag|USA}} \n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Philadelphia]]\n| 96,546,400\n| 327,700\n| {{convert|36.7|mi|km|sortable=on}}<ref name=\"SEPTA-Media\">{{cite web | url = http://www.septa.org/media/guide/pdf/media-guide.pdf | title = SEPTA \u2013 Media Guide | publisher = Southeastern Pennsylvania Transportation Authority | format = pdf | year = 2013 | accessdate = 2017-05-19}}</ref><ref name=\"SEPTA-Stats\">{{cite web |url=http://septa.org/strategic-plan/reports/route-statistics.pdf |title=SEPTA Route Statistics 2016 |publisher=Southeastern Pennsylvania Transportation Authority |format=pdf |year=2016 |accessdate=2017-05-19}}</ref>\n| 8,929\n| 1907\n| 75<ref name=\"SEPTA-OpFacts\">{{cite web |url=http://www.septa.org/strategic-plan/reports/opfacts.pdf |title=SEPTA Operating Facts Fiscal Year 2015 |publisher=[[SEPTA|Southeastern Pennsylvania Transportation Authority (SEPTA)]] |format=pdf |pages=4\u20136 |year=2015 |accessdate=2017-05-19}}</ref>\n| 3<ref name=\"SEPTA-OpFacts\" />\n|-\n| 12\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Port Authority Trans-Hudson|PATH]]\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | {{flag|USA}} \n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Jersey City]]\n| 91,593,600\n| 310,000\n| {{convert|13.8|mi|km|sortable=on}}<ref name=\"WTC-progress\">{{cite web |url=http://www.panynj.gov/wtcprogress/pdf/Feb2010-WTC-Progress-Newsletter.pdf |title=World Trade Center Progress |publisher=The Port Authority of New York and New Jersey |format=pdf |page=2 |date=February 2010 |accessdate=2014-08-31}}</ref>\n| 22,464\n| 1908\n| 13<ref name=\"PATH-map\">{{cite web |url=http://www.panynj.gov/path/maps-schedules.html |title=Maps & Schedules \u2022 Maps |publisher=The Port Authority of New York and New Jersey |date= |accessdate=2014-08-31}}</ref>\n| 5<ref name=\"PAT