a/ |title=Metro cambia patrones de consumo en Panam\u00e1 |newspaper=Capital Financiero |language=Spanish |trans-title=Metro changing consumption patterns in Panama |date=March 23, 2015 |accessdate=2015-04-01}}</ref>\n| {{convert|22.9|mi|km|sortable=on}}<ref name=\"Panama-L1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.elmetrodepanama.com/linea1.php |title=Conoce la L\u00ednea 1 del Metro de Panam\u00e1 |publisher=Metro de Panam\u00e1 |language=Spanish |trans-title=Meet Line 1 of the Panama Metro |year=2014 |accessdate=2014-08-31 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140503195921/http://www.elmetrodepanama.com/linea1.php |archivedate=2014-05-03 }}</ref>\n| 21,176\n| 2014\n| 12<ref name=\"Panama-map\">{{cite web|url=http://www.elmetrodepanama.com/pdf/LineaUno.pdf |title=L\u00ednea 1 Conoce los accesos a sus estaciones |publisher=Metro de Panam\u00e1 |language=Spanish |trans-title=Line 1 Explore access to stations |format=pdf |accessdate=2014-08-31 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150213071936/http://www.elmetrodepanama.com/pdf/LineaUno.pdf |archivedate=2015-02-13 }}</ref>\n| 1<ref name=\"Panama-map\" />\n|-\n| 15\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Santo Domingo Metro]]\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | {{flag|Dominican Republic}} \n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Santo Domingo, Dominican Republic|Santo Domingo]]\n| 61,270,054<ref name=\"Santo-Domingo\">{{cite web |url=http://opret.gob.do/Documentos/Estad%C3%ADsticas%20Institucionales/Informe%20Mensual%20de%20explotaci%C3%B3n%20%20Diciembre%202014.pdf |title=Informe de Evoluci\u00f3n de la Demanda Diciembre 2014 |publisher=Direcci\u00f3n de Operaciones Metro de Santo Domingo [Directorate of Operations Santo Domingo Metro] |via=http://opret.gob.do/Transparencia/Estadisticas.aspx |language=Spanish |trans-title=Report on Changes in Demand December 2014 |format=pdf |page=7 |date=January 7, 2015 |accessdate=2015-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402093659/http://opret.gob.do/Do